# Excelsior Fencing Club — public website

**GitHub:** `Excelsior-Fencing-Club/Excelsior-fencing-website`  
**Local:** `C:\Users\apeta\Documents\Repos\Excelsior\Excelsior-fencing-website`  
**Live site:** https://www.excelsiorfencing.ca (GitHub Pages)

This repo is an **Obsidian vault** (`.obsidian/`). It is **public-facing content only** — not board minutes, invoices, or VSC records.

## Sibling repo (internal ops)

| Repo | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| **Excelsior-Fencing-Club** | Board, grants, invoices, VSC, org docs |
| **Excelsior-fencing-website** (this repo) | Site pages, news, coaches, calendar |

Persistent agent rules for club ops live in the **club repo** `.cursor/rules/`. This repo’s rules cover **publishing and site structure**.

## Stack

- **Jekyll** on GitHub Pages
- Theme: `pages-themes/hacker@v0.2.0` (`_config.yml`, `jekyll-remote-theme`)
- Markdown + YAML frontmatter; Jekyll tags `{% include_relative ... %}`

## Top-level pages

`index.md` (home + recent news), `News.md` (archive), `Coaches.md`, `Calendar.md`, `Links.md`, `The_History_of_Fencing.md`, `images/`

When editing coaches or public copy, prefer this repo — not the club ops repo.
